        {
            "title": "民企座談會釋出正面訊號 召開後一年大市多向上 分析籲留意「兩會」發展",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"民企座談會釋出正面訊號 召開後一年大市多向上 分析籲留意「兩會」發展\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cd836a80b1789555fef2e385542ea3f1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250218/_2025021812050464178.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">民企座談會釋出正面訊號 召開後一年大市多向上 分析籲留意「兩會」發展</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>國家主席習近平昨日出席民企座談會，據證券界人士認為，此舉向外界釋出支持民企的正面訊號，去除政策不確定性，並有望提升市場風險胃納。\n\n</p><h2>集中AI及機器人等領域</h2>\n<p>據內媒報道，國盛證券首席經濟學家熊園指內地當局相隔7年再次召開民企座談會，是次更強烈展示穩定民營經濟的政策決心，除了強調自主可控，硬科技涉獵面亦不低，相信會集中人工智能、機器人、新能源及農業領域，市場可進一步留意3月份「兩會」發展。\n\n</p>\n<p>華創證券首席策略分析師姚佩認為，座談會召開後的一年，大市向上的機會很大，不但提升市場信心，亦有助社融及信貸改善。他續指，在參與發言的企業看，或呈現國產替代、製造業及科技向上的趨勢。\n\n</p><h2>去除政策不確定性憂慮</h2>\n<p>銀河證券發表報告指，在新一輪科技革命和民促法即將頒布下，座談會對民企實現高質量發展意義重大，有利提升微觀主體信心和市場風險偏好，去除市場對政策不確定性的憂慮。該行相信，今次將再度確立民企的經濟地位，是自去年一系列政策轉向以來，資本市場進入另一個轉捩點。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關文章：\n\n</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/macroeconomics/3429570\">習近平會晤科企巨頭 近7年第4次召開企業座談會 過往恒指兩升一跌</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053440/即時-財經-民企座談會釋出正面訊號-召開後一年大市多向上-分析籲留意-兩會-發展",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-18 12:11:46",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "英超｜里奧擔心曼聯真係會降班 預測最後13輪一場都贏唔到(附賽程)",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/407c4842831bfd8a06c0b3b0c2ba0a1d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250218/_2025021812053493577.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>曼聯目前只排英超第15位，陷降班危機。球會名宿里奧費迪南周一在個人網上頻道中直言擔心紅魔真的有機會降班，指球隊最後13輪英超不易踢，認為曼聯一場都贏唔到。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dbaa5622244e1587346f50841b77b85c/2025-02/2025-02-02T140725Z_1898159445_UP1EL22138CC1_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-CRY-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c7441e9d931764fcd86a1b3f7370df4a/2025-02/2025-02-02T153656Z_57069829_UP1EL2217DIJM_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-CRY-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯主帥魯賓艾摩廉。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/db45719cd1929111fccacfdcae126df2/2025-02/2025-02-02T160213Z_1108360927_UP1EL2218JOMG_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-CRY-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1f672fd4cd93ac3f96814717c3f14435/2025-02/2025-02-02T160518Z_1634198403_UP1EL2218OSMR_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-CRY-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯排英超第15位。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3e0c756b596147bd16afcf774de26b64/2025-02/2025-02-02T160144Z_1042324747_UP1EL2218IVMC_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-MUN-CRY-REPORT_1_.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3920e8cdddf15c732c791318ca9a215f/2025-02/2025-02-16T182450Z_1896839498_UP1EL2G1F5C5Q_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-TOT-MUN-REPORT_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51f60dda0ed81de65fba0b79c202efd5/2025-02/2025-02-16T182843Z_84862973_UP1EL2G1FBU6E_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-TOT-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aebcd801e0805ca7c9f8f695759dc29e/2025-02/2025-02-16T182928Z_1442198103_UP1EL2G1FD36L_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-TOT-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b43cf4dfa8cbb6ca669872dcd5c95f7a/2025-02/2025-02-16T183129Z_2123093537_UP1EL2G1FGF6S_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-TOT-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4b79d4a90da683148dc683567c91d88/2025-02/2025-02-16T183456Z_2107332572_RC2UVCA8L8RU_RTRMADP_3_SOCCER-ENGLAND-TOT-MUN-REPORT.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯表現奇差。Reuters\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>曼聯陷降班危機</h2>\n<p>曼聯今季英超表現奇差，尤其在新帥魯賓艾摩廉麾下一勝難求，在其帶領下14場英超只得4勝8負2和。球隊25輪後只得29分排第15位，離降班區只差2位，降班並非不可能。\n\n</p><h2>里奧預測最後13輪一場都贏唔到</h2>\n<p>球會名宿里奧費迪南擔心道：「曼聯現在的表現很掙扎，我們離降班區只差2位，真的很接近。有人說我們只需要多取11分就能護級，然後我認真地看了一下賽程表。作客愛華頓，還有作客車路士、諾定咸森林和紐卡素，另外又要對曼城、阿仙奴和阿士東維拉等。我認為只有一場曼聯有機會搶分，但也不一定能取得3分，就是作客李斯特城，因為我們今季已擊敗過他們3次。完全看不出有任何一場可輕鬆取勝，這令人擔心。」\n\n</p><h2>曼聯最後13輪賽程</h2>\n<p>客VS愛華頓<br/>\n主VS葉士域治<br/>\n主VS阿仙奴<br/>\n客VS李斯特城<br/>\n客VS諾定咸森林<br/>\n主VS曼城<br/>\n客VS紐卡素<br/>\n主VS狼隊<br/>\n客VS般尼茅夫<br/>\n客VS賓福特<br/>\n主VS韋斯咸<br/>\n客VS車路士<br/>\n主VS阿士東維拉\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2053441/即時-體育-英超-里奧擔心曼聯真係會降班-預測最後13輪一場都贏唔到-附賽程",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-18 12:11:47",
